gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Raptors 133, Warriors 118
gameRecap.excerpt: Led by RJ Barrett’s season-high 37 points, the Raptors defeated the Warriors, 133-118. Barrett added six rebounds, six assists and five 3PM, while Pascal Siakam added 16 points, six rebounds and six assists for the Raptors in the victory. Klay Thompson tallied 25 points (5-7 3PT FG) and three assists for the Warriors in the losing effort. The Raptors improve to 15-21 on the season, while the Warriors fall to 17-19.
